Directions
From North FL on I-95
Take I-95 South to FL 70 West/Okeechobee Rd. (exit 129).
Continue West on FL 70 West/Okeechobee Rd. for 32.1 miles.
Turn South (left) onto S Parrott Ave.
Continue to South on Parrott Ave for 3.1 miles.
Turn right onto FL-78 W.
Continue on FL-78 W for 24.4 miles.
Turn right onto Old Lakeport Rd NW.
Destination will be on the left.
Check-in parking
is on the left side of the street.
1073 Old Lakeport Rd
Moore Haven, Florida 33471
GPS: 26.974056,-81.11980
